name: Original Transmorpher
background: An epic W-Engine favored by Starlight Knight fans. Its high popularity and scarcity marketing strategy have caused an influx of knock-offs. "Using a fake transmorpher will only turn you into a villain's minion!" said its distributor at the product launch conference. Did you see that mighty kick that can send any evil-doer flying? Such is the power of the original product license!
skill: Increases Max HP by 8%/9%/10%/11%/12%. When attacked, the equipper's Impact is increased by 10%/11.5%/13%/14.5%/16% for 12s.
